Aula 1 - Exercício - 07/02/2017

Relacione cada chamada de sistema (system call) do padrão POSIX com as categorias abaixo:

Processos
.Statfs (2POSIX) .Fstatfs (2POSIX) .Getfsstat (2POSIX) .Listen (2POSIX) .Gethostname (2POSIX) .Lstat (2POSIX) .Mq_getattr (2POSIX) .Mq_close (2POSIX) .Mq_open (2POSIX) .Mq_receive (2POSIX) .Mq_send (2POSIX) .Mq_unlink (2POSIX) .Nfssvc (2POSIX) .Pipe (2POSIX) .Sethostname (2POSIX) .Sethostname (2POSIX) .Setrlimit (2POSIX) .Settimeofday (2POSIX) .Shm_unlink (2POSIX) .Shm_open (2POSIX) .shutdown(2POSIX)

Memória Principal
.Fpathconf (2POSIX) .Fsync (2POSIX) .Mmap (2POSIX) .Munmap (2POSIX) .Symlink (2POSIX)

Arquivos
.read(2POSIX) .Readv (2POSIX) .rename(2POSIX) .Rmdir (2POSIX) .Mount (2POSIX) .Chown (2POSIX) .Chroot (2POSIX) .Chmod (2POSIX) .Close (2POSIX) .Dup (2POSIX) .Dup2 (2POSIX) .Fchmod (2POSIX) .Fchown (2POSIX) .Fcntl (2POSIX) .flock(2POSIX) .Fstat (2POSIX) .Ftruncate (2POSIX) .Stat (2POSIX) .Statfs (2POSIX) .Ftruncate (2POSIX) .Getdirentries (2POSIX) .Getfh (2POSIX) .Gettimeofday (2POSIX) .Hostname (2POSIX) .Lseek (2POSIX) .open(2POSIX) .Truncate (2POSIX) .Umask (2POSIX) .Mkdir (2POSIX) .Mkfifo (2POSIX) .Mknod (2POSIX)

Sistema de E/S 
.select(2POSIX) .Swapon (2POSIX)

Armazenanmento Secundário
.Chdir (2POSIX) .Chroot (2POSIX) .Fchdir (2POSIX) .Link (2POSIX) .Sync (2POSIX) .unlink(2POSIX) .write(2POSIX) .writev(2POSIX)

Rede
.Accept (2POSIX) .Acesso (2POSIX) .bind(2POSIX) .Connect (2POSIX) .Getpeername (2POSIX) .Getsockname (2POSIX) .Getsockopt (2POSIX) .Recv (2POSIX) .Recvfrom (2POSIX) .Recvmsg (2POSIX) .send(2POSIX) .sendmsg(2POSIX) .Sendto (2POSIX) .Setsockopt (2POSIX) .socket(2POSIX) .Socketpair (2POSIX)
